{"lastModified":1775661073753,"uri":"c::7819240017::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: United States of America - New England, United States of America - North East\nWinter Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (US/British Virgin Islands), Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Virgin Islands (US), Caribbean Virgin Islands (British Virgin Islands)\n\nSOUTHERN BELLE (former Moon River, Anaisa) is a 26.52m / 87ft Luxury Motor Superyacht built in 2006 by Johnson. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 4. Cruising at 12.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 18.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a Master cabin with a king size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, a VIP cabin with a king size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, a cabin with a double bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, and a cabin with a twin bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"SOUTHERN BELLE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c2b9560-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c0ee5a0-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c292460-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c2ad210-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c0f81e0-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c30c580-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c124100-c71d-11f0-822d-d77140743cb1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cb501ba0-c719-11f0-b5bd-358e15f49545::assets::6c309e70-c71d-11f0-822e-d